Looks like a successful day to me.  How do you determine it's stocked, clipped pelvic fin?  The hump back and small head is stocked. Long nice sliver ones with all the fins is a natural.
They both look stocked. Looks like a adipose is clipped on the right one. Could be just be just the pic not showing it well.
Adipose was in place on the right one. The left one was missing one of the side fins.  Cheers, Ice Fisherman
